[color=orangered][u][b]DESCRIPTION[/b][/u][/color]

EaseUS MobiSaver for Android provides all-around solution to help Android users recover lost SMS, contacts, pictures, audio, videos and documents from Android Phone, tablets or SD cards inside Android device.	
Key Features:
1. Retrieve lost SMS, contacts, photos, videos, audio, documents from Android devices and SD card.
2. Recover Android data lost after deletion, formatting, restoring factory setting, rooting, etc.
3. Available for multiple Android OS and Android devices, such as Samsung, LG, HTC, Motorola, Sony, Google, etc.
4. Support to preview all the recoverable data before recovery. Allow to selectively recover the specific files you want to get back.
